<!--


Come to think of it, instead of having regular braindead zombies, why not steal Earthdawn's Cadaver Men? Superficially, they look the same. Key difference is that Cadaver Men retain their sentience; they've just lost the ability to feel anything but pain. This causes them to turn insane, of course, and they hate the living for, well, being more fortunate than themselves. Causing pain to the living temporarily eases their own pain. But unlike regular zombies, they can be talked to, if not reasoned with.

vampires based on the seven deadly sins?


